  ],
  "notes": [
    "This is a Metabase collection export template for CIRL analytics.",
    "",
    "Before importing:",
    "1. Set up your Athena connection in Metabase (see docs/06-bi-integration.md)",
    "2. Create the Athena views (metrics_clean, conversations_clean, operators_clean)",
    "3. Replace {{ATHENA_DATABASE_ID}} with your Metabase database ID for Athena",
    "4. Replace 'your-tenant-id' with your actual tenant ID in all queries",
    "",
    "To import:",
    "1. Go to Admin → Tools → Import in Metabase",
    "2. Upload this JSON file",
    "3. The collection will be created with all questions and dashboards",
    "",
    "Note: Metabase's import/export format may vary by version.",
    "This template is compatible with Metabase v0.40+.",
    "You may need to manually recreate questions if import fails."
  ]
}
